name: Arca Gajah Mungkur
description: Gajah Mungkur is the name given to the reservoir with the legend of the power struggle that occurred between Gajah Mego and Gajah Mungkur. In the fight, the two people turned into elephants. Patih Gajah Mungkur won the fight. The former battle arena is believed to be the location of the Gajah Mungkur Reservoir.
